rows.label: qst700404_msg0001
rows.name:
Mooooo!? You defeated
the Gogols for us, mo?

rows.label: qst700404_msg0002
rows.name:
Amazing, mo! You all are
truly, truly heroes, mo!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0003
rows.name: I can't just stand here, mo... Popolo!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0004
rows.name:
Yes, mo! I will report
to everyone at once...

rows.label: qst700404_msg0005
rows.name: I'm heading out for a bit, mooooo!!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0006
rows.name: Momomoo!? Are you going yourself, mo!?

rows.label: qst700404_msg0007
rows.name:
...So that's how it is, mo! Thanks
to these people, we can use the
oasis just like before, mo.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0008
rows.name: It's all right now, mooo!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0009
rows.name:
Thank you! Now we can
transport goods with ease!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0010
rows.name:
You saved us, mo! We won't
forget this kindness, mooo!!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0011
rows.name: No, we only did what was natural...

rows.label: qst700404_msg0012
rows.name:
To find such amazing people, the
chairman really is incredible.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0013
rows.name:
That's for sure. With the chairman
around, the shopping ward is safe.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0014
rows.name:
Chairman-san, please visit my
shop again! I have some special
sweet potatoes for you.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0015
rows.name:
While you're at it, please check
out our new products too!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0016
rows.name:
Ah, you're cheating, mo! Us too!
I want you to see ours too, mo!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0017
rows.name: M-Me too!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0018
rows.name: W-W-Wait, don't push, mo!

rows.label: qst700404_msg0019
rows.name: Wow... he's so popular.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0020
rows.name:
He must be an excellent merchant
and a person of character as well.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0021
rows.name:
...Everyone looks so happy.
This is nice, isn't it?

rows.label: qst700404_msg0022
rows.name: Fufu...

rows.label: qst700404_msg0023
rows.name:
Hugo, when you look at the
townspeople, you have such a
gentle look in your eyes.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0024
rows.name: Eh? Is... that so?

rows.label: qst700404_msg0026
rows.name: Does something bother you, Minochi?

rows.label: qst700404_msg0027
rows.name:
No, it's just that I'm the
type who doesn't believe
in people of character.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0028
rows.name:
...Harsh, for a blade
of Deacon Marveni.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0029
rows.name:
Hmph. It doesn't matter if you're human
or Blade. Whether for good or bad, a
large imbalance creates distortion.

rows.label: qst700404_msg0030
rows.name: I just hope nothing happens...
